# Enterprise Credit Knowledge Framework (ECKF)

Status: **ENTERPRISE APPROVED** · Phase 1 foundation

## What it is

Premium enterprise **knowledge portal** for credit underwriting architecture.

## What it is NOT

- Not a calculation engine
- Not a lender eligibility engine
- Not a policy simulator
- Not AI / matching / decisioning

## Hierarchy (frozen)

Master Product → Customer Category → Credit Programs → Lender Variations

Never design lender-first.

## Phase 1

Home Loan only. Future products plug into the same navigator + section framework without redesign.

## Source of truth

- Types: `src/types/enterprise-credit-knowledge-framework.ts`
- Constants / Home Loan blueprint: `src/constants/enterprise-credit-knowledge-framework`
- UI: `EckfKnowledgeWorkspace`
- Route: `/admin/credit-knowledge-framework`
